{"title":"The Wake Was a Line and We Watched","author":{"name":"Mary Jo Bang"},"publishDate":"2010-10-13","lines":[{"line":"While we stood in the window and wept.","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"Well, not wept but sniveled","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"A little and wiped our eyes","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"On a coat sleeve. What","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"Were we thinking, I wonder now.","stanza":2,"number":5},{"line":"It was fall.","stanza":2,"number":6},{"line":"It was clear. A boat sat","stanza":2,"number":7},{"line":"Throwing a reflection of itself","stanza":2,"number":8},{"line":"Onto a body of water.","stanza":3,"number":9},{"line":"It sits and sits. As the ornament is","stanza":3,"number":10},{"line":"A monument so is the bird in the sky","stanza":3,"number":11},{"line":"One with the eyes","stanza":3,"number":12},{"line":"That were taking it all in.","stanza":4,"number":13},{"line":"An argument for a theory","stanza":4,"number":14},{"line":"Of all-in-oneness. All as all. Imagine","stanza":4,"number":15},{"line":"The “I” as a camera turned on","stanza":4,"number":16},{"line":"To a mirror.","stanza":5,"number":17},{"line":"Where the face in the mirror","stanza":5,"number":18},{"line":"Isn’t that of the one looking in","stanza":5,"number":19},{"line":"But of Jacqueline Onassis","stanza":5,"number":20},{"line":"Or someone else famous","stanza":6,"number":21},{"line":"Beyond saying.","stanza":6,"number":22},{"line":"A full fifteen minutes.","stanza":6,"number":23},{"line":"It’s in the nature of looking","stanza":6,"number":24},{"line":"At the future while married to the moment.","stanza":7,"number":25},{"line":"It’s Disney’s “Mickey","stanza":7,"number":26},{"line":"And The Broken Mirror Mishap”","stanza":7,"number":27},{"line":"All over again.","stanza":7,"number":28},{"line":"The jagged glass reforming","stanza":8,"number":29},{"line":"Into a narrative where","stanza":8,"number":30},{"line":"The core event keeps clicking into place","stanza":8,"number":31},{"line":"As a great, a terrible, shattering.","stanza":8,"number":32},{"line":"This thought leads straight","stanza":9,"number":33},{"line":"To the darkest thought: I miss home.","stanza":9,"number":34},{"line":"Like a child misses home, or","stanza":9,"number":35},{"line":"A line drawing of a Quebec Marmot.","stanza":9,"number":36},{"line":"That’s what happens.","stanza":10,"number":37},{"line":"Meanwhile, the madness.","stanza":10,"number":38},{"line":"The brain-gray concourse.","stanza":10,"number":39},{"line":"The utter factuality of the few true things.","stanza":10,"number":40}]}